{"tid":1869562,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"警喬裝送貨員 指控藏丫叉彈珠作非法用途 22歲男今獲撤控","createTime":"2020-02-08T08:53:11.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-08T09:08:22.000Z","uid":296607,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"abee6003ef29be99cd498894b5e845ae1ced7540","tid":1869562,"uid":296607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-08T08:53:11.000Z","msg":"警喬裝送貨員 指控藏丫叉彈珠作非法用途 22歲男今獲撤控<br />\n<br />\n報導：<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2H1OLDh\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2H1OLDh&d=KH9yB5wEnJvJbT5Qn4WrOirXKCTJ71YGEIw5q99tfRY%3D&h=a1f3092a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2H1OLDh</a><br />\n<br />\n一名22歲的男子，於去年11月11日「三罷」中被控襲警及管有攻擊性武器。海關於同月26日截查他的一個包裹，懷疑他管有丫叉及彈珠作非法用途，警員喬裝送貨員上門，拘捕了他的母親，及後乘他到警署報到時再拘捕他。<br />\n<br />\n控方今在九龍城裁判法院申請撒回控罪，獲裁判官批准，趙獲當庭釋放。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nSource from: <br />\n香港獨立媒體網<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/inmediahknet\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Finmediahknet&d=KH9yB5wEnJvJbT5Qn4WrOirXKCTJ71YGEIw5q99tfRY%3D&h=1ff68f4c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/inmediahknet</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n手足已被還押<span style=\"color: red;\">72日先</span>黎撤控，但我仲未搵到楊大狀個deadbody<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"375a79a405d79677cc72d61468bf7b759975bb5c","tid":1869562,"uid":40745,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-08T08:55:11.000Z","msg":"都算好消息<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ed953120b08f3edefde9b5deb029cab54daf972","tid":1869562,"uid":296607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-08T09:03:15.000Z","msg":"唔知手足有無打訴告黑驚"},{"pid":"18b5082381e26af82f05c676aa55b78e920072e3","tid":1869562,"uid":136797,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-08T09:08:22.000Z","msg":"失去左咁多日自由邊個賠"}]}